Manchester City striker John Guidetti is wanted by Feyenoord who are prepared to sign him on a permanent deal.

The Swedish international had a successful loan spell with the Dutch club in 2011/12.

Juventus have also shown an interest in the 22-year-old who is available for around £4.5million.

